    "The preliminary knowledge is introduced in Section 2, covering prompting and efficiency.",
    "This is followed by a detailed discussion of hard prompt methods in Section 3 and soft prompt methods in Section 4.",
    "The key elements driving the evolution of prompt compression models are examined, and insights into various methods are provided.",
    "Their downstream adaptations are discussed in Section 5 as well.",
    "Finally, Section 6 analyzes the challenges of current prompt compression techniques and proposes several potential solutions."
